  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554520/extras/6cf80d855dcdc5002f827141e3056e2c.poster.avif?t=1748704554\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554520/extras/6cf80d855dcdc5002f827141e3056e2c.webm?t=1748704554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554520/extras/6cf80d855dcdc5002f827141e3056e2c.mp4?t=1748704554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Smackball</strong> is a fast-paced, competitive sports game for two players, inspired by sports like tennis, squash and air-hockey. The rules are simple: smack the ball across half court before your timer runs out, and try to score a goal against your opponent!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play locally, against your friends or the AI.<br></li><li> Play online, in private matches against your friends, or match up against random players.<br></li><li> 5 different game modes.<br></li><li> 8 color palettes to personalize the look of the game.<br></li><li> Customize the gameplay and create your own game modes.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Note:</h2>You’ll need at least one controller for local multiplayer matches.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554520/extras/6cf80d855dcdc5002f827141e3056e2c.poster.avif?t=1748704554\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554520/extras/6cf80d855dcdc5002f827141e3056e2c.webm?t=1748704554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554520/extras/6cf80d855dcdc5002f827141e3056e2c.mp4?t=1748704554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Smackball</strong> is a fast-paced, competitive sports game for two players, inspired by sports like tennis, squash and air-hockey. The rules are simple: smack the ball across half court before your timer runs out, and try to score a goal against your opponent!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play locally, against your friends or the AI.<br></li><li> Play online, in private matches against your friends, or match up against random players.<br></li><li> 5 different game modes.<br></li><li> 8 color palettes to personalize the look of the game.<br></li><li> Customize the gameplay and create your own game modes.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Note:</h2>You’ll need at least one controller for local multiplayer matches.",
